description:
Perform a security audit of the Nx Witness VMS system (https://localhost:7001) to identify configuration gaps. Identify cameras with recording disabled, cameras not included in any layout, and users with no layouts assigned or shared. Generate a JSON report saved to /home/ga/coverage_gap_report.json with the following structure:
{
  "report_timestamp": "<ISO 8601 string>",
  "system_name": "<System Name>",
  "total_cameras": <int>,
  "total_users": <int>,
  "total_layouts": <int>,
  "gaps": {
    "cameras_not_recording": [ {"id": "...", "name": "..."} ],
    "cameras_not_in_any_layout": [ {"id": "...", "name": "..."} ],
    "users_without_layouts": [ {"id": "...", "name": "..."} ]
  },
  "summary": {
    "cameras_not_recording_count": <int>,
    "cameras_not_in_any_layout_count": <int>,
    "users_without_layouts_count": <int>
  }
}
Credentials: admin / Admin1234! (Token available in /home/ga/nx_token.txt).
